{"service_name": "Hortonworks Hadoop Developer Training: Apache Pig and Hive", "service_id": "7361311410396080", "company_name": "Big Data Partnership Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Big Data Partnership Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Hortonworks Hadoop Developer Training: Apache Pig and Hive\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    This 4 day training course is designed for developers who need to create applications to analyse Big Data stored in Apache Hadoop using Pig and Hive. Topics include: Hadoop, YARN, HDFS, MapReduce, data ingestion, workflow definition and using Pig and Hive to perform data analytics on Big Data.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Software developers who need to develop applications for Hadoop\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     50% Hands-On Labs &amp; 50% Lecture/Discussion\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Certification preperation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Private on-site\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Public course schedule available\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Labs are executed on a 7-node HDP cluster\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Virtual Instructor-led training available\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Become a proven expert in Apache Pig &amp; Hive\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ability to develop solutions on Hadoop\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Describe Hadoop, YARN and use cases for Hadoop\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Describe Hadoop ecosystem tools and frameworks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Describe the HDFS architecture\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Use HCatalog with Pig and Hive\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Run MapReduce and YARN application jobs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Use advanced Hive features: windowing, views, ORC files\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a32195 per person\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Education pricing available\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Other\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/587241/7361311410396080-pricing-document-2015-10-06-1210.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/587241/7361311410396080-service-definition-document-2015-10-06-1150.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/587241/7361311410396080-terms-and-conditions-2015-10-06-1154.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-headin